                                            "text": "创建实体类图",
                                            "note": "在`docs`中添加实体类，如\n\n```mermaid\nclass 01user~用户~{\n\ttext fld1~alias1~key\n\ttext fld2~alias2~key\n\tsmallint fld3~alias3~\n\tint fld4~alias4~\n\tbigint fld5~alias5~\n\tjbonb fld6~alias6~\n}\n```\n"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "d18zdlbbf080",
                                            "created": 1715650592020,
